1
00:00:17,350 --> 00:00:18,727
Terima kasih sudah datang!

2
00:01:54,531 --> 00:01:55,365
{\an8}TOKO SAKAMOTO

3
00:01:55,448 --> 00:01:57,951
{\an8}Pak Sakamoto, kau keren sekali kemarin!

4
00:01:58,034 --> 00:01:59,119
{\an8}DAYS.2
VS. SON HEE DAN BACHO

5
00:01:59,202 --> 00:02:01,788
Pertarungan jarak dekatnya keren sekali!

6
00:02:01,871 --> 00:02:03,289
Aku baru melihat yang begitu!

7
00:02:03,373 --> 00:02:06,876
Meski sudah pensiun,
kau tetap yang terbaik!

8
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:09,587
Pukul seperti ini, lalu membalas!

9
00:02:09,671 --> 00:02:10,505
<i>Kembali bekerja.</i>

10
00:02:10,588 --> 00:02:13,174
Sebagian besar kau bunuh
dengan sekali pukul!

11
00:02:13,258 --> 00:02:14,092
Apa?

12
00:02:14,801 --> 00:02:15,802
"Bunuh"?

13
00:02:16,594 --> 00:02:17,637
Sayang,

14
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:20,849
kau tidak menjadi
pembunuh bayaran lagi, 'kan?

15
00:02:23,852 --> 00:02:26,521
Namun, kau membunuh
mereka semua waktu itu.

16
00:02:26,604 --> 00:02:28,064
Kupastikan tidak fatal.

17
00:02:28,148 --> 00:02:31,359
Sayang, apa kau harus diingatkan?

18
00:02:32,235 --> 00:02:35,196
Kita bercerai jika kau melanggar
aturan keluarga kita.

19
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,365
Bercerai!

20
00:02:41,786 --> 00:02:43,496
Bagus jika kau mengerti.

21
00:02:43,997 --> 00:02:46,124
Aku akan menyapu di luar.

22
00:02:49,252 --> 00:02:51,588
"Aturan keluarga" apa?

23
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:58,386
Berhenti membunuhku dalam pikiranmu!

24
00:02:58,469 --> 00:03:00,388
<i>Jangan membicarakan hal tak penting.</i>

25
00:03:01,097 --> 00:03:02,348
PECINAN NIIKITA

26
00:03:03,933 --> 00:03:07,604
Rupanya ini Pecinan Niikita!

27
00:03:07,687 --> 00:03:09,188
Luas sekali!

28
00:03:09,981 --> 00:03:13,985
{\an8}Namun, kenapa jauh-jauh kemari
untuk membeli barang toko?

29
00:03:16,779 --> 00:03:17,989
Terima kasih!

30
00:03:19,782 --> 00:03:21,784
<i>Hanya ada 50 per hari!</i>

31
00:03:21,868 --> 00:03:23,036
"Bakpao Babi Surga?"

32
00:03:23,119 --> 00:03:25,246
Apa ini alasanmu kemari?

33
00:03:25,330 --> 00:03:27,707
<i>Cukup untuk Aoi dan Hana juga.</i>

34
00:03:32,670 --> 00:03:36,424
<i>Dia sangat menyayangi keluarganya!</i>

35
00:03:36,507 --> 00:03:40,345
{\an8}Omong-omong, apa "aturan keluarga"
yang Bu Aoi bicarakan?

36
00:03:40,428 --> 00:03:41,304
<i>Diam.</i>

37
00:03:41,387 --> 00:03:43,348
Tak perlu kau jelaskan, pikirkan saja!

38
00:03:43,431 --> 00:03:44,891
Aku tinggal membaca pikiranmu!

39
00:03:46,309 --> 00:03:48,311
{\an8}Minggir!

40
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:53,107
Pak Sakamoto!

41
00:03:55,818 --> 00:03:57,320
BAKPAO BABI SURGA

42
00:03:58,738 --> 00:04:00,615
Bakpao Babi Surga-nya!

43
00:04:01,699 --> 00:04:03,785
Jika dibersihkan, mungkin masih...

44
00:04:04,911 --> 00:04:06,287
Ternyata tidak.

45
00:04:06,788 --> 00:04:07,830
Itu dia!

46
00:04:07,914 --> 00:04:09,916
- Berengsek!
- Tangkap dia!

47
00:04:12,085 --> 00:04:14,128
{\an8}GADIS MISTERIUS
LU SHAOTANG

48
00:04:14,212 --> 00:04:17,507
Kau pikir bisa lolos
dengan menyelinap seperti kucing?

49
00:04:17,590 --> 00:04:20,385
Tak mungkin aku tertangkap
orang bodoh seperti kalian!

50
00:04:20,468 --> 00:04:24,472
Pak Sakamoto?
Mungkin sebaiknya kita pergi sebelum...

51
00:04:25,098 --> 00:04:26,349
<i>Sudah hancur.</i>

52
00:04:30,395 --> 00:04:33,189
Maaf, ini bukan waktunya mencemaskan itu!

53
00:04:40,822 --> 00:04:42,865
<i>Dia bisa taici!</i>

54
00:04:42,949 --> 00:04:44,325
Kepung dia!

55
00:04:53,918 --> 00:04:54,752
Dasar kau...

56
00:05:01,342 --> 00:05:03,469
Kena kau.

57
00:05:03,553 --> 00:05:05,680
Hei! Lepaskan aku!

58
00:05:08,057 --> 00:05:09,934
Beri pelajaran, tapi jangan dibunuh.

59
00:05:11,769 --> 00:05:13,980
Mulai dari kakimu
agar kau tidak bisa kabur.

60
00:05:22,238 --> 00:05:24,157
Siapa pria itu?

61
00:05:28,786 --> 00:05:31,372
Diam! Jangan bergerak!

62
00:05:31,456 --> 00:05:33,082
- Gawat!
- Kubunuh...

63
00:05:49,098 --> 00:05:51,392
<i>Siapa gadis ini?</i>

64
00:05:51,476 --> 00:05:53,269
Lihat, itu dia!

65
00:05:53,352 --> 00:05:55,730
Dia membawa teman! Habisi mereka!

66
00:05:55,813 --> 00:05:57,440
"Teman?"

67
00:05:58,149 --> 00:05:59,484
Ayo kabur!

68
00:05:59,567 --> 00:06:00,443
Kejar mereka!

69
00:06:00,526 --> 00:06:01,861
Jangan lari!

70
00:06:03,321 --> 00:06:04,572
Kalian siapa?

71
00:06:05,615 --> 00:06:06,824
Sial!

72
00:06:10,453 --> 00:06:11,788
PT DAN

73
00:06:11,871 --> 00:06:13,414
Di mana gadis itu?

74
00:06:13,998 --> 00:06:16,125
Sepertinya dia kabur...

75
00:06:16,751 --> 00:06:19,253
Ada dua pria yang membantunya kabur.

76
00:06:19,337 --> 00:06:21,380
Kami sedang mencari tahu tentang mereka.

77
00:06:22,298 --> 00:06:24,675
Kau membiarkannya lolos lagi?

78
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,843
{\an8}DIRUT PT DAN

79
00:06:25,927 --> 00:06:30,306
Kita membunuh seluruh klannya
demi melacaknya!

80
00:06:30,389 --> 00:06:33,851
Jika dia menghilang, itu semua sia-sia!

81
00:06:33,935 --> 00:06:35,269
Dasar bodoh!

82
00:06:35,853 --> 00:06:37,355
Mohon maaf, Pak!

83
00:06:37,438 --> 00:06:38,773
Cukup!

84
00:06:38,856 --> 00:06:40,108
Enyahlah!

85
00:06:41,984 --> 00:06:43,194
Panggil mereka.

86
00:06:43,277 --> 00:06:44,403
Baik...

87
00:06:52,787 --> 00:06:57,875
Lihat, Son Hee,
kepalanya masih terengah-engah!

88
00:06:58,459 --> 00:06:59,961
Dasar bodoh...

89
00:07:00,044 --> 00:07:02,171
Jangan bermain dengan mayat.

90
00:07:02,255 --> 00:07:04,882
Itu tindakan kotor, Bacho.

91
00:07:06,134 --> 00:07:08,136
<i>Dua bersaudara ini gila...</i>

92
00:07:08,219 --> 00:07:09,428
Dengar.

93
00:07:09,512 --> 00:07:12,515
Kami butuh kunci gadis itu.

94
00:07:12,598 --> 00:07:14,475
Setelah mendapat kunci itu,

95
00:07:14,559 --> 00:07:16,811
kami bisa menguasai seluruh pasar gelap!

96
00:07:16,894 --> 00:07:19,605
Aku tidak peduli caranya. Temukan dia!

97
00:07:19,689 --> 00:07:23,609
Berarti kami boleh membunuh
siapa pun yang menghalangi, 'kan?

98
00:07:24,610 --> 00:07:25,945
Lakukan sesuka kalian.

99
00:07:29,407 --> 00:07:30,408
Apa?

100
00:07:30,491 --> 00:07:32,201
Kau putri keluarga mafia?

101
00:07:32,285 --> 00:07:35,037
Bukan keluarga mafia biasa,
tapi klan Lu yang terkenal?

102
00:07:35,121 --> 00:07:36,831
Jangan ucapkan begitu keras!

103
00:07:36,914 --> 00:07:39,041
Mereka mau apa darimu?

104
00:07:40,501 --> 00:07:42,295
Benda ini.

105
00:07:42,378 --> 00:07:43,296
Kunci?

106
00:07:43,379 --> 00:07:46,340
Kunci brankas tersembunyi klan kami.

107
00:07:46,424 --> 00:07:47,967
Orang tuaku memercayakannya.

108
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:50,678
Lupakan itu, buang saja.

109
00:07:50,761 --> 00:07:52,513
Itu tidak sepenting nyawamu.

110
00:07:53,139 --> 00:07:54,640
Tidak akan!

111
00:07:56,642 --> 00:07:57,768
Ayahku dan ibuku

112
00:07:58,811 --> 00:08:00,771
tewas demi melindungi kunci ini.

113
00:08:05,526 --> 00:08:07,778
Shaotang, kau pergi dahulu!

114
00:08:08,738 --> 00:08:10,656
Cepat! Pergi!

115
00:08:18,331 --> 00:08:20,541
Jika kubiarkan mereka mengambilnya,

116
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:23,961
bagaimana aku bisa
menghadapi mereka di surga?

117
00:08:25,379 --> 00:08:28,799
Sudahlah. Ini bukan masalah kalian.

118
00:08:28,883 --> 00:08:30,676
Maaf sudah merepotkan!

119
00:08:34,055 --> 00:08:35,598
Ini waktunya berpisah.

120
00:08:37,099 --> 00:08:40,144
Apa kau tahu
cara membuat bakpao babi asli?

121
00:08:40,728 --> 00:08:42,688
Apa? Bakpao babi?

122
00:08:43,272 --> 00:08:47,985
Ayahku mengajarkanku dasarnya,
kurasa aku bisa.

123
00:08:48,069 --> 00:08:51,531
Pak Sakamoto, jangan terlibat!

124
00:08:51,614 --> 00:08:53,741
Firasatku buruk tentang gadis ini.

125
00:08:53,824 --> 00:08:56,244
Batalkan berbelanja hari ini.

126
00:08:57,078 --> 00:08:58,496
Kita selamatkan dia.

127
00:09:00,081 --> 00:09:04,168
Namun, kau harus membuatkan kami
bakpao babi setelah kau aman.

128
00:09:04,252 --> 00:09:05,628
Sepakat?

129
00:09:05,711 --> 00:09:08,297
Apa? Kalian berdua...

130
00:09:09,966 --> 00:09:10,925
Pak Sakamoto!

131
00:09:19,809 --> 00:09:21,227
Pak Sakamoto!

132
00:09:21,310 --> 00:09:23,688
Mereka mengejar selagi kita berbicara.

133
00:09:24,272 --> 00:09:25,231
Selain itu,

134
00:09:25,898 --> 00:09:28,150
sepertinya ini makin gawat.

135
00:09:29,193 --> 00:09:33,239
Bacho, sudah kubilang, caramu itu kotor.

136
00:09:33,322 --> 00:09:38,119
Diam. Tidak ada yang namanya bersih
dalam dunia pembunuh.

137
00:09:38,202 --> 00:09:40,830
Jika terlihat, langsung kita bunuh.

138
00:09:40,913 --> 00:09:43,874
Jika kau mau, kita bisa
menjajarkan mayat mereka dengan rapi.

139
00:09:43,958 --> 00:09:46,961
Maksudku caramu membunuh.

140
00:09:47,461 --> 00:09:49,880
Rasanya seperti bicara dengan monyet.

141
00:09:49,964 --> 00:09:51,841
Siapa mereka?

142
00:09:51,924 --> 00:09:54,093
Son Hee dan Bacho.

143
00:09:54,176 --> 00:09:55,720
Mereka pembunuh bayaran kembar.

144
00:09:56,637 --> 00:10:00,600
<i>Mereka meminta bayaran yang gila,
tapi tidak pernah gagal.</i>

145
00:10:00,683 --> 00:10:04,478
<i>Mereka pembunuh berantai
yang senang membunuh orang.</i>

146
00:10:04,562 --> 00:10:07,857
<i>Hobi mereka membuat sketsa kepala korban.</i>

147
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:09,317
<i>Mereka gila!</i>

148
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:12,153
Kurasa kita sudah terkenal.

149
00:10:12,236 --> 00:10:13,863
Bukankah itu bagus, Son Hee?

150
00:10:13,946 --> 00:10:15,197
Dasar bodoh.

151
00:10:15,281 --> 00:10:16,824
Kita pembunuh bayaran.

152
00:10:16,907 --> 00:10:18,993
Seharusnya kita tidak menarik perhatian.

153
00:10:19,076 --> 00:10:21,203
Seharusnya begitu!

154
00:10:23,247 --> 00:10:26,292
Kau marah karena temanmu kami bunuh?

155
00:10:26,375 --> 00:10:28,669
Sepertinya gadis kecil di sini
bukan hanya Lu.

156
00:10:28,753 --> 00:10:30,963
Kau kira kau membunuh temanku?

157
00:10:31,505 --> 00:10:33,132
Kau pasti sangat bodoh.

158
00:10:35,593 --> 00:10:39,180
Hanya pembunuh bayaran amatir
yang tidak tahu Taro Sakamoto.

159
00:10:39,847 --> 00:10:41,432
Bicaralah selagi bisa, Nak.

160
00:11:03,245 --> 00:11:04,538
Bajingan...

161
00:11:05,164 --> 00:11:06,791
Siapa kau?

162
00:11:12,129 --> 00:11:14,423
<i>Bakpao kacang merah juga enak.</i>

163
00:11:26,227 --> 00:11:27,520
<i>Di mana ini?</i>

164
00:11:28,854 --> 00:11:30,272
{\an8}TUTUP

165
00:11:30,356 --> 00:11:34,151
Pria itu cukup kuat.

166
00:11:34,235 --> 00:11:35,736
Benar, Bacho?

167
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:39,782
Atapnya pasti mulai rapuh.

168
00:11:40,366 --> 00:11:42,493
Aku akan menghancurkannya.

169
00:11:42,576 --> 00:11:43,702
Gadis kecil.

170
00:11:44,787 --> 00:11:48,958
Serahkan kuncinya
jika mau mati dengan elegan.

171
00:11:49,041 --> 00:11:49,959
Sepakat?

172
00:11:50,042 --> 00:11:52,211
Hanya ini peninggalan dari orang tuaku...

173
00:11:52,753 --> 00:11:55,214
Sampai mati pun tak akan kuserahkan!

174
00:11:55,297 --> 00:11:57,216
Astaga.

175
00:11:57,299 --> 00:12:01,053
Orang tuamu juga mengucapkan itu
sebelum aku menghabisi mereka.

176
00:12:01,971 --> 00:12:03,389
Sayang sekali.

177
00:12:03,472 --> 00:12:06,517
Kau lebih mementingkan benda
daripada nyawamu?

178
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,894
Menjijikkan sekali.

179
00:12:08,978 --> 00:12:09,979
Diam!

180
00:12:10,688 --> 00:12:11,689
Jangan!

181
00:12:16,193 --> 00:12:17,361
Beraninya kau!

182
00:12:17,445 --> 00:12:20,739
Dasar bodoh.
Jangan terpancing oleh mereka.

183
00:12:22,199 --> 00:12:27,538
Brankas itu menyimpan semua keinginan
dan harapan leluhurku selama ini.

184
00:12:28,205 --> 00:12:29,999
Ayahku tewas demi melindunginya.

185
00:12:30,666 --> 00:12:32,209
Karena para bajingan itu...

186
00:12:32,293 --> 00:12:33,419
Baiklah.

187
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:38,632
Ayolah, jangan mengganggu!

188
00:12:39,216 --> 00:12:42,887
Dia hampir bertemu
orang tuanya yang tercinta lagi.

189
00:12:42,970 --> 00:12:47,016
Tidak ada yang berhak menentukan
yang penting atau tidak bagi orang lain.

190
00:12:50,102 --> 00:12:51,437
Kenapa...

191
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:54,899
Kenapa kau membahayakan dirimu
demi menolongku?

192
00:13:06,368 --> 00:13:07,995
Kau berlumuran darah lagi...

193
00:13:08,829 --> 00:13:10,456
Aku harus bekerja...

194
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:14,043
"Bekerja"? Maksudmu "membunuh"!

195
00:13:14,126 --> 00:13:16,086
Kenapa kau melakukan hal sekejam itu?

196
00:13:17,171 --> 00:13:19,673
Aku harus bekerja
agar bisa membelikanmu hadiah...

197
00:13:19,757 --> 00:13:23,093
Aku tidak mau hadiah
yang berlumuran darah seperti itu!

198
00:13:25,846 --> 00:13:27,181
Sudah cukup.

199
00:13:29,517 --> 00:13:32,144
Jika kau tidak bisa berubah,

200
00:13:32,228 --> 00:13:33,354
kurasa...

201
00:13:34,813 --> 00:13:36,023
kita tidak bisa bersama.

202
00:13:37,066 --> 00:13:37,942
Selamat tinggal.

203
00:13:47,368 --> 00:13:48,744
- Ada yang jatuh!
- Apa?

204
00:13:55,501 --> 00:13:57,753
Ternyata lebih tinggi dari dugaanku!

205
00:13:57,878 --> 00:14:00,130
Syukurlah saljunya tebal!

206
00:14:01,882 --> 00:14:03,133
Lihat?

207
00:14:03,217 --> 00:14:07,763
Kau akan sedih jika aku mati, 'kan?

208
00:14:08,889 --> 00:14:09,765
Mengerti?

209
00:14:09,848 --> 00:14:13,269
Perasaan yang membuatmu
ingin menyelamatkanku

210
00:14:13,352 --> 00:14:17,022
juga dirasakan oleh semua orang.
Semua orang disayangi oleh seseorang.

211
00:14:18,482 --> 00:14:20,901
Jadi, berjanjilah...

212
00:14:25,281 --> 00:14:26,991
kau tidak akan membunuh lagi.

213
00:14:27,741 --> 00:14:29,451
Itu aturan kita.

214
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,204
Demi menebus orang-orang yang kau bunuh,

215
00:14:32,288 --> 00:14:33,497
mulai sekarang,

216
00:14:34,582 --> 00:14:36,917
hiduplah menyelamatkan orang lain.

217
00:14:43,173 --> 00:14:44,675
Sudah berhenti berdarah.

218
00:14:45,384 --> 00:14:47,595
Dilarang membunuh. Paham, Shin?

219
00:14:48,429 --> 00:14:50,139
Ya, Pak Sakamoto!

220
00:14:50,222 --> 00:14:53,100
Jangan terlalu percaya diri, dasar amatir!

221
00:15:08,407 --> 00:15:09,241
Rasakan ini!

222
00:15:27,384 --> 00:15:29,219
Hebat juga.

223
00:15:32,181 --> 00:15:34,725
Bacho, pikiranmu sama denganku?

224
00:15:34,808 --> 00:15:37,478
Tentu, Kak. Ayo!

225
00:15:42,775 --> 00:15:44,652
Teknik Besi Tuang,

226
00:15:45,194 --> 00:15:46,612
Tebasan Neraka!

227
00:15:48,989 --> 00:15:51,033
Jadilah daging cincang!

228
00:15:54,995 --> 00:15:55,913
Apa?

229
00:15:57,289 --> 00:15:59,291
Kau tidak apa-apa, Pak Sakamoto?

230
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:01,043
<i>Kurasa leherku terkilir.</i>

231
00:16:01,627 --> 00:16:03,170
Ini, pakai koyok.

232
00:16:03,253 --> 00:16:06,715
<i>Dia... menghindari semua itu?</i>

233
00:16:06,799 --> 00:16:09,385
<i>Padahal, Tebasan Neraka
tak bisa dihindari!</i>

234
00:16:09,468 --> 00:16:11,387
<i>Apalagi dengan tubuh sebesar itu.</i>

235
00:16:11,470 --> 00:16:13,597
<i>Bagaimana bisa?
Dia tak terluka sama sekali!</i>

236
00:16:14,682 --> 00:16:17,309
Bacho, pikiranmu sama denganku?

237
00:16:17,393 --> 00:16:19,687
Tentu, Kak. Ayo!

238
00:16:21,021 --> 00:16:23,899
Kau orang ketiga yang melihat ini!

239
00:16:25,567 --> 00:16:27,236
Teknik Besi Tuang!

240
00:16:33,826 --> 00:16:35,327
Bajingan!

241
00:16:39,707 --> 00:16:43,293
<i>Cakramku yang sudah diperkuat!</i>

242
00:16:43,377 --> 00:16:45,087
<i>Siapa pria ini?</i>

243
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:51,468
<i>Aku tidak terbiasa dengan beratnya.</i>

244
00:16:51,552 --> 00:16:52,428
<i>Sakit.</i>

245
00:16:52,553 --> 00:16:54,596
Pak Sakamoto, pakai ini di tanganmu.

246
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:58,308
<i>Sial! Lupakan mereka.</i>

247
00:16:59,018 --> 00:17:00,686
<i>Aku akan mengincarnya saja!</i>

248
00:17:00,769 --> 00:17:02,646
Aku mendengarnya!

249
00:17:11,321 --> 00:17:12,990
{\an8}BANTINGAN KEREN
TUMBUKAN KULKAS!

250
00:17:22,374 --> 00:17:25,627
Siapa kalian berdua sebenarnya?

251
00:17:30,424 --> 00:17:32,134
Hanya karyawan toko biasa.

252
00:17:34,136 --> 00:17:37,264
Aku benar-benar tidak paham.

253
00:17:37,347 --> 00:17:41,018
Sial! Di mana Bacho dan Son Hee?

254
00:17:41,101 --> 00:17:43,937
Padahal harta karunnya
hanya di balik pintu ini!

255
00:17:44,605 --> 00:17:48,108
Aku cuma butuh kunci itu. Kunci kecil itu!

256
00:17:48,192 --> 00:17:49,401
Ada kiriman!

257
00:17:52,154 --> 00:17:53,906
Bacho! Son Hee!

258
00:17:54,782 --> 00:17:56,575
Siapa kalian?

259
00:17:56,658 --> 00:17:58,494
Apa yang kalian lakukan kepada...

260
00:17:58,577 --> 00:17:59,661
Diam.

261
00:17:59,745 --> 00:18:00,913
Tutup mulutmu.

262
00:18:00,996 --> 00:18:02,998
Kau!

263
00:18:04,541 --> 00:18:06,585
Maaf! Maafkan aku!

264
00:18:06,668 --> 00:18:09,463
Aku akan melakukan apa pun! Kumohon!

265
00:18:09,546 --> 00:18:12,758
"Maaf" saja tak bisa
mengembalikan orang tuaku!

266
00:18:13,383 --> 00:18:15,219
Bertobatlah di neraka!

267
00:18:24,394 --> 00:18:26,271
Kau yakin itu cukup?

268
00:18:26,355 --> 00:18:28,398
Mungkin pukul beberapa kali lagi...

269
00:18:31,401 --> 00:18:33,695
Jangan membunuhku dalam pikiranmu!

270
00:18:33,779 --> 00:18:35,656
<i>Jangan ikut campur.</i>

271
00:18:38,325 --> 00:18:39,660
Ini cukup.

272
00:18:41,829 --> 00:18:45,165
Kita tak boleh membunuh
setiap kali ada yang membuat kita kesal.

273
00:18:45,249 --> 00:18:47,876
"Pilihlah hidup yang bahagia."

274
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:49,419
Ayahku selalu mengatakan itu.

275
00:18:54,967 --> 00:18:57,177
Masih belum, Rambut Merah Muda?

276
00:18:57,302 --> 00:18:59,847
Diam, Orang Tidak Sopan!

277
00:18:59,930 --> 00:19:02,558
Namaku Lu Shaotang.

278
00:19:03,183 --> 00:19:05,811
Kuncinya sudah tua, sulit diputar.

279
00:19:08,981 --> 00:19:10,440
Akhirnya!

280
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:11,650
Apa isinya?

281
00:19:11,733 --> 00:19:13,694
Hei, seharusnya aku dahulu!

282
00:19:15,404 --> 00:19:18,740
Lihat harta karunnya!

283
00:19:19,908 --> 00:19:22,744
Ada buku juga? CD? Boneka?

284
00:19:23,453 --> 00:19:25,080
Koleksi yang aneh...

285
00:19:25,831 --> 00:19:28,167
Lihat, ada inventori.

286
00:19:29,918 --> 00:19:31,295
Coba lihat.

287
00:19:31,378 --> 00:19:37,009
"Kepala klan Lu harus meninggalkan
harta paling berharganya di brankas ini."

288
00:19:37,092 --> 00:19:40,387
Sepertinya harta karun
setiap kepala klan berbeda.

289
00:19:41,138 --> 00:19:42,764
Apa yang ditinggalkan ayahku?

290
00:19:50,189 --> 00:19:51,315
Apa tulisannya?

291
00:19:52,274 --> 00:19:55,986
<i>"Minuman untuk diminum bersama Shaotang
saat dia sudah cukup umur."</i>

292
00:19:57,863 --> 00:19:59,406
<i>Ayah memang seperti ini.</i>

293
00:20:00,407 --> 00:20:03,035
Ayolah. Apa tulisannya?

294
00:20:04,995 --> 00:20:08,290
Katanya ini miras paling enak di dunia!

295
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:10,792
Cobalah! Sebagai tanda terima kasih.

296
00:20:12,628 --> 00:20:14,838
Sebaiknya benar-benar enak!

297
00:20:17,507 --> 00:20:20,677
Pak Sakamoto, kau masih membawanya?

298
00:20:20,761 --> 00:20:23,597
Apa ini? Kenapa semuanya hancur?

299
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:25,557
Karena kau.

300
00:20:26,183 --> 00:20:28,018
<i>Namun, masih enak.</i>

301
00:20:33,523 --> 00:20:36,193
Bakpao babi Jepang ternyata lumayan.

302
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:10,620
<i>Kemarin, di Pecinan Niikita,</i>

303
00:22:10,704 --> 00:22:14,624
<i>diduga terjadi perkelahian
antara anggota mafia.</i>

304
00:22:14,708 --> 00:22:15,625
<i>Menurut para saksi...</i>

305
00:22:15,709 --> 00:22:17,294
Selamat pagi!

306
00:22:17,377 --> 00:22:18,962
<i>Berisik.</i>

307
00:22:19,046 --> 00:22:21,590
<i>Sakit kepala, pengar...</i>

308
00:22:22,716 --> 00:22:24,760
Minum ini, Pak Sakamoto.

309
00:22:24,843 --> 00:22:25,886
JUS JERUK

310
00:22:25,969 --> 00:22:27,054
Selamat...

311
00:22:27,929 --> 00:22:30,140
Bos, apron ini pas sekali.

312
00:22:30,223 --> 00:22:32,225
Sedang apa kau di sini?

313
00:22:32,309 --> 00:22:35,812
Aku menganggur.
Aku akan membuat bakpao babi asli di sini.

314
00:22:35,896 --> 00:22:38,607
Namun, kau punya segudang harta karun!

315
00:22:38,690 --> 00:22:42,486
Aku tidak mau menggunakan
warisan keluargaku. Apa kau bodoh?

316
00:22:43,195 --> 00:22:44,321
Apa katamu?

317
00:22:44,404 --> 00:22:46,031
Otak lambat?

318
00:22:46,114 --> 00:22:48,658
<i>Tolong... jangan berisik.</i>

319
00:22:48,742 --> 00:22:52,704
Omong-omong,
aku benar-benar tersentuh oleh ceritamu.

320
00:22:52,788 --> 00:22:55,040
Alasanmu berhenti membunuh.

321
00:22:55,832 --> 00:22:56,792
<i>Dari mana kau tahu?</i>

322
00:22:58,085 --> 00:23:00,879
Saat kita melawan para penjahat itu,

323
00:23:00,962 --> 00:23:03,924
aku melihat kenangan
yang kau pikirkan, lalu...

324
00:23:05,634 --> 00:23:07,969
Sekarang itu juga berlaku untukmu.

325
00:23:08,053 --> 00:23:08,970
ATURAN KELUARGA

326
00:23:10,222 --> 00:23:11,181
Baik.

327
00:23:14,726 --> 00:23:17,687
"Aturan pertama. Jangan membunuh."

328
00:23:17,771 --> 00:23:19,481
{\an8}<i>Kubunuh kau jika kau langgar.</i>

329
00:23:19,564 --> 00:23:21,358
{\an8}Berarti kau juga melanggarnya!

330
00:23:27,114 --> 00:23:29,074
Dari JAA.

331
00:23:29,157 --> 00:23:30,158
DICARI

332
00:23:30,242 --> 00:23:34,121
Uang hadiah si gemuk ini...

333
00:23:34,204 --> 00:23:35,747
satu miliar yen.

334
00:23:35,831 --> 00:23:37,374
Terjemahan subtitle oleh Sudirman Lius

